<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1922-07-05T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1922-07-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="853" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d853">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">837.513/54: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Representative on Special Mission in Cuba</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Crowder</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-07-05"><hi rend="italic">July 5,
                                1922</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>39. Your 41, June 30, 5 p.m.</p>
                        <p>Department desires to commend you for the admirable way in which you have
                            handled the negotiations and for the results obtained.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
